
Version 1.1
-----------

* Allow update of registered systems (fs backend only)
* Configuration moved to a single external file
* Available callbacks for :
  - nagios - services to be monitored
  - stats-collector - metrics to be collected
  - cobbler
* Improved documentation
* Include packaging for rpm and dpkg formats


Version 1.0
-----------

* Register systems
* Apache authentication module for systems and users
* Keep track of system aliveness using nagios
* Two filesystem backends (filesystem and berkeley DB)

